<BLOCK1><TI TOCID="II">JUDGMENT</TI>
<P><BOLD>THE TRIAL</BOLD> of this action was heard on April 17 and 18, 2018 at the Court House at 393 University Avenue, Toronto, Ontario.</P>
<P><BOLD>ON READING</BOLD> the pleadings and hearing the evidence of the witnesses called to give evidence at trial and on reading the written submissions of counsel for the parties, the decision having been reserved until May 25, 2018;</P>
<P><BOLD>AND ON READING</BOLD> the written submissions of counsel for the parties on the issue of costs, the decision on that issue being reserved until August 15, 2018;
<P1><BOLD>1. THIS COURT ORDERS AND ADJUDGES</BOLD> that the defendant shall pay to the plaintiff the sum of $69,091.12 for damages in lieu of notice of termination; and</P1>
<P1><BOLD>2. THIS COURT ORDERS AND ADJUDGES</BOLD> that the defendant shall pay to the plaintiff her costs of the action in the all-inclusive amount of $15,000.00 for fees, disbursements and applicable taxes;</P1></P>
<P>This Judgment bears interest at the rate of 3 % (a) on the amount set out in paragraph 1 above from May 25, 2018 and (b) on the amount set out in paragraph 2 above from August 15, 2018.</P>
<P>&ellip35;</P>
