<P>19. 3395022 ceased operations on December 31, 2011 and a Certificate of Dissolution was issued in respect of the corporation on May 7, 2012. The plaintiff was issued a Record of Employment.
<P1><BOLD>Certificate of Dissolution, Exhibit 24, Appeal Book and Compendium, Tab 8&ndash;24, p. 200</BOLD></P1>
