<P>28. On December 20, 2012 the plaintiff was given notice of the termination of her employment, with Kutcher Dentistry Professional Corporation, effective that day and was further advised that she would be provided payment in lieu of notice and her final pay, including payment for the day on which the termination occurred, plus her vacation pay to the end of the notice period, in accordance with the terms of her employment agreement. She was again provided with a Record of Employment.
